= He lands it — rough, and alive. TO WRITE — new bar.

## 18. AFTERMATH

= The honest reckoning: the arrest, the court. Reyes keeps her word; the suspended sentence holds; the cage is avoided. TO WRITE — new bar.

## 19. CODA

= The recordings of his gentle voice become the thing strangers pass around — a living folk hero this time, not a tragic one. He and Maya, the pills and the silence between them, begin to talk. It ends on a changed man choosing the ordinary life he almost left. TO WRITE — new bar.
